casebody.data:
No. 11-560. Mariana Leger, Warden, Louisiana Correctional Institute for Women, Petitioner v. Princess P. Lacaze. 565 U.S. 1174, 132 S. Ct. 1137,

181 L. Ed. 2d 1009,

2012 U.S. LEXIS 598. January 17, 2012.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 645 F.3d 728.
